{"tid":1961500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普盼本月底解除社交限制　期望英國首相約翰遜早日康復","createTime":"2020-04-06T23:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T23:15:58.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eecb3c78e833da8871f1ae5aaa12d6b9b23ca66c","tid":1961500,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T23:15:41.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，希望在本月底可以解除社交限制。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮表示，紐約州和新澤西州將開始使用醫療船，治療新型肺炎確診患者。特朗普又表示，他早前與民主黨的前副總統拜登通電話15分鐘，討論疫情，特朗普形容對話非常好，拜登提出他的觀點，他表示理解。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又對接受深切治療的英國首相約翰遜致以慰問，表示美國人都會祈求約翰遜早日康復。"},{"pid":"5bbf558a6fe5051d28dbcbdc4b9ac2f58e7fb445","tid":1961500,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T23:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519248-20200407.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519248-20200407.htm&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2leyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=679623a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519248-20200407.htm&h=e189ffd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519248-20200407.htm</a>"}]}